                     <interp inst="t18170702-13-person153" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
            . I am a hosier, and live in the Strand. I saw the prisoner take the handkerchief out of Mr. Richter's pocket. I am sure he is the man. I told Mr. Richter, and he pursued him.</p>
               <p>(Property produced and sworn to.)</p>
               <p>Prisoner. I beg for mercy.</p>
